text: Tariq Haroon (born 3 February 1977) is a Pakistani cricketer. He has played in 77 first-class and 56 List A cricket matches since 2000. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Karachi cricketers Category:Karachi Blues cricketers Category:Karachi Dolphins cricketers Category:Pakistan Customs cricketers Category:Cricketers from Karachi
